projects.name: Gambia River Solar Power
projects.description: A renewable energy initiative aiming to harness solar power along the Gambia River. The project involves installing solar panels to provide sustainable and reliable energy to nearby villages, enhancing local energy independence and reducing reliance on fossil fuels.

projects.name: Sustainable Agriculture Enhancement
projects.description: Aimed at improving agricultural practices in The Gambia through the introduction of sustainable farming techniques. This includes training farmers in water-efficient irrigation, organic farming, and crop rotation to boost yields and ensure food security.

projects.name: Educational Infrastructure Development
projects.description: A project to construct and renovate schools in rural and underserved areas of The Gambia. It focuses on creating accessible, well-equipped educational facilities to improve literacy rates and educational outcomes.

projects.name: Gambia Digital Literacy Drive
projects.description: Focused on enhancing digital literacy and access to technology in The Gambia. This includes setting up computer labs in schools, providing internet access, and training teachers and students in digital skills.
